{"tid":1313068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"善用沙田市中心區域嘅兩層結構","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:43:33.000Z","uid":75514,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d3d0e7665e7f395c160f08155703409d44254a","tid":1313068,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"高層：商場同天橋，由希爾頓中心一直連到去瀝源再到禾輋<br />\n低層：地面<br />\n<br />\n高層同低層之間有好多上落位，好難數晒，舉幾個例：<br />\n1. 沙田市中心巴士總站<br />\n2. 偉華中心電梯<br />\n3. 新城市中心大會堂出口<br />\n4. 好運中心商場入面嘅樓梯同電材<br />\n5. (極隱蔽) 好運中心後樓梯，上層入口係越北牛肉粉隔離，下層入口係甜品舖隔離道閘<br />\n6. 沙田中心電梯同樓梯<br />\n7. 瀝源邨現代教育門口條樓梯 + 商場附近幾條樓梯<br />\n<br />\n就咁google map好難睇到條路，總之有咩事向瀝源禾輋方向走會容易啲走到，因為嗰邊多巷仔<br />\n<br />\n另外，盡頭嘅禾輋邨入面，地面基本上係迷宮嚟，以前陳根記大排檔附近D路只要唔係禾輋人基本上係好難認<br />\n沿車路可以入火炭<br />\n沿山路可以上穗禾苑<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce17f12fe6e8fd59bda00b717b560fdcaebf898","tid":1313068,"uid":277155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"沙田區一日遊？多謝分享"},{"pid":"57d5d9aaf5353f07eed7620639a39766aa65bed5","tid":1313068,"uid":277155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223928aa8c6011eff045ae12281c3fdc0d7d4a41","tid":1313068,"uid":164372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd3e85a3aaee19efa101d24e27c19435911b3f1","tid":1313068,"uid":272775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdf284efcfe285b99eb18f572131f2ff2291b5c","tid